data.description: Calling all Investors and/or Homebuyers looking for a property that needs some work. Welcome to 4332 Westglen! This home requires some TLC. It's perfect for an investor or buyer interested in making repairs to fit your taste and budget. Main level entails a family room with a fireplace, dining room, kitchen and three bedrooms, with two full bathrooms. The lower level offers a family space and powder room. The backyard is spacious and ideal for entertaining. Property is being sold As Is.
